The name of the boy is written in an elegant calligraphic script. All text can be personalized and has a golden color similar to the faux gold crest. The background is royal blue.

The vintage floral crest from an old book cover binding, of the book "Rust, Smut Mildew & Mould", from 1870, now in the public domain. Price:$2.00
